          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1617713476284-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, drain the<strong> potatoes</strong> (reserve the pot for later!) and shake them around the colander to fluff the edges up a little</p><p>Add the <strong>fluffed potatoes</strong> to a large baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1617713492587-x200.jpg",
