          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1617713492587-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have had 10 min, add the <strong>sliced carrot</strong> and <strong>halved green beans </strong>to the tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 10 min</p><p>Meanwhile, crush the<strong> garlic cloves</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1617713524607-x200.jpg",
