            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add 2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> with the <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil and cook for 5-6 min or until thickened, then set aside for later – this is your<strong> garlic-infused gravy</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1617713548712-x200.jpg",
