            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1617713548712-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the gravy is thickening, top the <strong>pork loin steaks</strong> with the<strong> herby crumb</strong></p><p>Tip: Press the crumb into the pork steaks firmly with your hands to help it stick!</p><p>Once the veg has had 10 min, add the <strong>herb-crusted pork steaks</strong> to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 13-15 min or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
